'''Charles L. Sawyers''' is a physician-scientist at [[Memorial Sloan-Kettering Cancer Center]]. He holds the Marie-Josee and [[Henry R. Kravis]] [[Chair (academic)|Chair]] in Human [[Oncology]] and [[Pathogenesis]] Program, and is also an investigator of the [[Howard Hughes Medical Institute]]. He won the 2009 [[Lasker Award|Lasker Clinical Award]].

